Package com.varmateo.yawg.spi

Interfaces and classes required for writing Yawg extensions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BakerService
    A baker of files.
    BakerServiceFactory
    A factory of BakerService instances.
    DirBakeListener
    Interface for objects that want to be notified when one given directory is baked during the baking procedure.
    DirBakeListenerFactory
    A factory of DirBakeListener instances.
    Template
    Layout template for a baked page.
    TemplateService
    Provider of layout templates for baking.
    TemplateServiceFactory
    A factory of TemplateService instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PageContext
    Information to be used by a baker when baking a file.
    PageContext.Builder
    A builder of PageContext instances.
    TemplateDataModel
    Data available to a template during processing.
    TemplateDataModel.Author
    Document author data.
    TemplateDataModel.Builder
    Builder of TemplateDataModel instances.
